snippet.textDisplay: For someone who grew up with the old FF and need for speed underground games it's just sad to see where this franchise has gone to. Of course things change but come on...at some point it's just ridiculous how far they've strayed away. What if James bond suddenly went full street racing with his Aston Martin talking about family? Sure it might be fun to watch but it's not what you associate him with. To all the street racing fans, it's time to grow up and start becoming spies who defy the laws of physics and logic...
